_______________________________

Episode 8
The Great British Bake Off: An Extra Slice, Series 2

It is the quarter finals in the Bake Off tent and just five bakers remain.

Jo Brand hosts An Extra Slice and is joined by three celebrity Bake Off fans to dissect this week's events in the tent, with unseen footage from the BBC One show and an interview with the latest baker to leave. They will taste bakes brought in by the studio audience and look at viewer photos of their bakes from home - the delicacies and the calamities.

How do the panel think the bakers coped with cream horns in the Signature? What did they make of the mokatines Technical? Had the panel even heard of the Showstopper - religieuse a l'ancienne? And which of the bakers do our panel think will make it through to the end?

An Extra Slice - when just one helping of Bake Off just isn't enough
